channel.title: Unexpected Response from Server. Help?
channel.description: I had just had a problem in NPCSpawn.cfg, and I fixed it. But after i compiled that update, when I log in, I get a message says "unexpected response from server". In The run.cmd, it says that it's reviving connections from me. But it keeps saying Unexpected response from server. The source I am using is Paladino76 based. If you could, please send me a link to another 508 source. thank you.
